{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"086c701d95","title":"139号犯人狱中报告（两枚镍币）","origin":"李辉整理《赵丹自述》，大象出版社，2003年1月第一版。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"056de12dd5","index":0,"year":1968,"month":12,"day":13,"articleId":"086c701d95"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"b5d30cfdb0","name":"赵丹"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"076a13dc7f","type":"title","text":"139号犯人狱中报告（两枚镍币）","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"086c701d95"},{"id":"8c99426a8d","type":"authors","text":"赵丹","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"086c701d95"},{"id":"ced9946162","type":"appellation","text":"这两枚一分钱的镍币是从哪儿来的呢？我记不确切了。记得我初到此地购买东西时，确是找分币零钱的。记得当时因为天冷，我曾要求过此地的工作人员代购些水果糖，好增加些热量，可工作人员不肯。而买东西改做只找糖、不找分币那是后来的事了。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"086c701d95"},{"id":"ed96ccff8f","type":"appellation","text":"我这个人在生活小事上，素来是马马虎虎，所以不知怎么就遗留下这两枚一分钱的镍币了。这实在是没有任何用意和用心在内的。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"086c701d95"},{"id":"09ff5c9cc1","type":"appellation","text":"在此认罪，并恳宽恕是幸！","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"086c701d95"},{"id":"5224419cdf","type":"paragraph","text":" 139","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"086c701d95"},{"id":"ff21c29117","type":"paragraph","text":" 一九六八年十二月十三日","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"086c701d95"}],"page":{"id":"29e1b1be5c","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"086c701d95","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}